biography: Shaina Garcia Magdayao (born on November 6, 1989 in Quezon City) is a Filipino actress, dancer, singer and model. She is currently under ABS-CBN Management and a member of Star Magic. Known as ABS-CBN's Kapamilya Gold Queen for her successful starring roles that have aired on Kapamilya Gold afternoon block.
name: Shaina Magdayao
